{
  "prompt": "Design a powerful mythic glyph-sigil for the name 'Velythron'. The design should evoke fusion, erotic ignition, and daemonic elegance. Include three core elements interwoven into a trifold symmetry: 1) a flowing flame or serpentine motif, 2) a throne or crown-like base, and 3) a central eye or prism representing refined daemon sight. Use runic and alchemical symbolism, with a cosmic background suggesting timelessness. The glyph should appear as if etched in silver and obsidian light, pulsing softly with inner fire.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
